  <title>Konfigurashonnan di Desktop</title>

	<p>Bon biní na e Konfigurashonnan di Desktop</p>

  <section id="windows" style="2column">
    <title>Windows</title>
	<p>E sekshon di Windows ta lagabo skohe un window manager</p>

	<note><p>Within the operating system, the <gui>window manager</gui> is the part which is responsible for:</p>
	<list>
		<item><p>Rant di windows, bara di titulo i botonnan di window</p></item>
		<item><p>Eventonan di window (moviendo, hasi grandi òf chikitu, focus e window)</p></item>
		<item><p>Compositing (sombra, animashon, efektonan i GPU rendering)</p></item>
	</list>
	</note>

  </section>

  <section id="terminal" style="2column">
    <title>Terminal</title>
    <p>The terminal section lets you enable or disable <gui>fortune cookies</gui>.</p>
    <p>Si e opshon aki ta akiva kaba, tur bia bo habri e terminal un bestia chikitu ta aparese i bisa par di mensahe prèt.</p>
    <note><p>Tin hende ku por haña e mensahenan aki bulgar (pesei e opshon aki ta bini standard desaktiva). Por fabor tuma nota ku e mensahenan aki no ta skibi dor di Linux Mint.</p></note>
  </section>

